<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Will you be attending The Conference Board in San Diego on March 27th and 28th? If so, I would love to schedule time to catch up.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">For some background, Livongo is a consumer digital health company that empowers all people with chronic conditions, starting with diabetes, to live better and healthier lives. Here are some recent updates on Livongo:</font></div><div style=""><ul><li><b>We’ve proven our approach to chronic conditions management:</b> Our members love us! We have an NPS of 64, which compares to companies like Netflix and Amazon. Also, our members are getting healthier while our clients are saving. <a href="https://www.livongo.com/news/livongo-demonstrates-cost-savings-for-employers/">Members are showing a .9% reduction in A1c, and clients have demonstrated a cost savings of $83pppm.</a></li><li><b>We’re expanding to heart disease:</b> we hired renowned cardiologist, Dr. Bimal Shah, to lead our expansion to heart disease, starting with hypertension, and we will launch Livongo for Hypertension to our existing members early this year.</li><li><b>We have almost 300 enterprise clients:</b> We are working with the leading Fortune 100 employers, the largest PBMs, 4 of 7 most innovative health plans, and leading health systems.</li><li><b>Our team is growing:</b> Arnnon Geshuri, formerly of Tesla, recently joined as Chief People Officer</li></ul></div><div style=""><font face="arial">While at the conference, we would love to see you at Livongo’s session, Proving Financial Impact and Business Model for Chronic Condition Management, on March 27th from 3:00 pm - 3:50 pm. Livongo Chief Commercial Officer, Jim Pursley, will join Magda Rusinowski, PepsiCo Director of US Health Benefits, as they discuss Livongo’s clinical outcomes and measurable financial impact.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Looking forward to hearing back from you and I hope we can connect while in San Diego.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Best regards,</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style=""><div style=""><br></div></div></div>]]></td>
